# Optional deployment wiring for the ficta proxy.
#
# A local/isolated POC normally needs no package .env file: `ficta setup` writes policy to
# ~/.ficta/config.toml. Start with docs/poc-configuration.md and use config.toml.example only when
# you need the complete advanced reference. Do not commit real secrets.

# Use a non-default persistent config file.
# FICTA_CONFIG_FILE=/etc/ficta/config.toml

# Change the proxy listener only when the deployment requires it. Loopback is the safe default.
# FICTA_HOST=127.0.0.1
# FICTA_PORT=8787
